direct your attention to the field.

55:34.251 --> 55:36.670
It is time for our charity partner
of the night.

55:36.712 --> 55:39.506
Julia has a long way to go
on her path to wellness,

55:39.548 --> 55:41.300
and we need your help.

55:41.341 --> 55:44.928
Please Google Julia Bruzzese
on GoFundMe,

55:44.970 --> 55:47.139
and be as generous as you can.

55:57.107 --> 56:00.235
- Support Julia Bruzzese
