01:09:58.740 --> 01:10:00.032
Try and hold it.

01:10:00.075 --> 01:10:01.952
Try and bring it out
towards me.

01:10:02.911 --> 01:10:04.204
Bring it out.

01:10:05.621 --> 01:10:07.165
Try and bring it out.

01:10:07.207 --> 01:10:09.585
Out.
Try and take it in.

